CYBER BALL

in 2077 the world is on the verge of collapse, the air is terrible. To stay healthy, sports are needed, one of which is playing basketball, but basketball at that time was very different from today. players are filled with hardware devices attached to their bodies, a fun basketball game turns into a game of life and death.
